       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. COMPLEX01.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 WS-PROGRAM PIC X(8) VALUE 'SUBPGM1'.
       COPY NESTCPY.
       >>IF DEFINED(TESTMODE)
       01 TEST-FLAG PIC X VALUE 'Y'.
       >>ELSE
       01 TEST-FLAG PIC X VALUE 'N'.
       >>END-IF
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       MAIN-LOGIC.
           MOVE 'SUBPGM2' TO WS-PROGRAM.
           CALL WS-PROGRAM.
           IF CARD-AMOUNT > 1000
              MOVE 'BLOCKED' TO CARD-STATUS
           END-IF.
           COMPUTE CARD-AMOUNT = CARD-AMOUNT * 1.05.
           PERFORM VALIDATE-LOGIC.
           GO TO EXIT-LOGIC DEPENDING ON CARD-COUNT.
       VALIDATE-LOGIC.
           EVALUATE CARD-STATUS
             WHEN 'A' CONTINUE
             WHEN OTHER MOVE 'INVALID' TO CARD-STATUS
           END-EVALUATE.
       EXIT-LOGIC.
           GOBACK.
